#Text=BDSM as business : Interviews with Dominatrixes
#Text=Sunday , October 28 , 2007
#Text=Whether the Civil War , World War II or the Iraq War , it can be challenging to face how conflict penetrates the psyche of a nation and surfaces in the nuances of life .
#Text=There are thousands — if not millions — of individuals who indulge in fantasies others would deem perverse that have their nascence in some of the darkest moments of human history .
#Text=It is possible someone you know pays a person to dress like a German Nazi to treat them like a “ dirty Jew ” , or to force them to pick cotton off the floor like a slave .
#Text=An S&M dungeon is a place where these individuals act out such taboos .
#Text=Businesses that operate to meet their needs are often hidden , but they do exist and are typically legal .
#Text=The clients want to remain confidential for fear of ostracism in their respective communities .
#Text=As Sigmund Freud wrote , " Anyone who has violated a taboo becomes taboo himself because he possesses the dangerous quality of tempting others to follow his example . "

column1: #Text=Last week Wikinews published the first in a two part series on the BDSM business : an interview with Bill & Rebecca , the owners of Rebecca ’s Hidden Chamber .
#Text=This week we publish the second part : an interview with three dungeon employees , Mistress Alex , Mistress Jada and Mistress Veronica .
#Text=In their world , BDSM is a game , a harmless pursuit of roleplaying exercises that satiate the desires of the tabooed .
#Text=These Dominatrixes are the kind of women men fantasize about , but they all look like they could be babysitting your children this Saturday night .
#Text=Most likely , they will not be .
#Text=Mistress Alex has a distinctive sheen when David Shankbone walks into the room .
#Text=Her moist skin cools quickly from the blow of the air conditioner she stands in front of .
#Text=Just having finished an hour and a half session , she is dressed in a latex one-piece skirt and matching boots .
#Text=Mistress Jada , a shapely Latina dressed in red , joins the conversation and remains throughout .
#Text=When Alex needs to tend to a client , Mistress Veronica , who looks like she would be as comfortable teaching kindergarten as she would " tanning a man 's hide " , takes over for her .
#Text=The interview was neither sensational nor typical , but what you read may surprise , repulse , or even awaken feelings you never knew you had .
#Text=Below is David Shankbone 's interview with three Dominatrixes .
#Text=Starting out
#Text=How did you get started as an S&M Mistress ?
#Text=I ’m from California and I started out by playing in various fetish clubs and I had different play partners .
#Text=I just kind of dabbled in my personal life .

#Text=When I moved to New York a few years ago , I was doing the same thing with friends and I realized I was getting bored hanging out with the same people all the time — they became good friends , but I met another pro-dom .
#Text=I was talking to her about it and realized I could end up experiencing so many different things in a place like this .
#Text=And it ’s true .
#Text=I meet so many different people who are into all these different things .
#Text=I ’m all about variety .
